genresAdvancedInfo.name: rap nortista
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Rap nortista is a style of rap music that originated in the northern regions of Brazil. It is heavily influenced by traditional northeastern music, such as forró and baião, and often incorporates elements of reggae and funk. The lyrics often address social and political issues, as well as the struggles of everyday life in the region.
